d to a 95 ct loss last year Nimocks said Peschs revised offer is not worth much more than the 20 dlrs cash offered previously But Feinberg said there is a better chance a transaction could be completed because of the revised structure of the offer I think its much more doable he said Analysts have said American Medical has begun a turnaround by replacing some members of management and reducing costs
