o asked not to be named Another analyst noted the price of Hk Hotels had been distorted by the takeover talks because its net asset value is only worth about 50 dlrs a share The offers by Evergo and Lai Sun were for 53 dlrs a share though that is well below the current trading price Trading was suspended today in shares of Lai Sun Evergo China Entertainment and the groups associate ltChinese Estates Ltd Chinese Estates lost 25 cents to 2015 dlrs yesterday China Entertainment five to 860 dlrs and Evergo one to 74 cents Lai Sun gained 50 cents to 7050 dlrs
