 acquisition of 30 pct or more of the companys voting stock Conrac said Treasurer Joseph Smorada and Vice President Joseph ODonnell who made 143325 dlrs last year would get one-and-a-half times his salary if there were a change in control Smoradas salary was not listed in the SEC filing The executives would also get cash settlements of options plans and continuation of insurance and other benefits
